///Keyword Research for YouTube///////////

Way-1
-	Go to “youtube.com”
-	Search : type your keyword (interior design)
 
-	For more search use star sign (*) in key word
Example:   
interior * design
interior house * design
Way-2
Use “Keyword Tool io”
-	Open browser 
-	Type : Keyword Tool io
-	Click on “keywordtool.io”
 
-	Click on “YouTube”
-	Search: interior design (your keyword)
-	Country: United States
-	Language: English
-	Click on “Search icon” button
-	Copy keywords
-	Paste in excel file
-	Analysis the best keyword from the list
Tips
-	Connect VPN if your market place is suppose United States
-	Search keywords in youtube.com

Way 3
Get keywords from other competitor videos
-	Go to youtube.com
-	Search: type your keyword (interior design)
-	Select a top beautiful video
-	Click on the video
-	When video playing, stop it
-	Right click on any place view page source
-	Ctrl + F
-	Type: key  (enter)
-	Search keywords
-	Copy keywords from contents
 
Way 4
